T1  - A personalized medicine approach to ovulation induction/ovarian stimulation: development of a predictive model and online calculator from level-I evidence.
T3  - Comment in: Fertil Steril. 2022 Feb;117(2):419-420. doi: 10.1016/j.fertnstert.2021.12.011 PMID: 34980429 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/34980429]
