T1  - Can hysterosalpingo-foam sonography replace hysterosalpingography as first-choice tubal patency test? A randomized non-inferiority trial.
T3  - Comment in: Hum Reprod. 2022 Jul 30;37(8):1953-1954 PMID: 35713336 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/35713336] Comment in: Hum Reprod. 2022 Jul 30;37(8):1952-1953 PMID: 35713337 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/35713337]
