T1  - Metformin and health outcomes: An umbrella review of systematic reviews with meta-analyses.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1111/eci.13536
A1  - Li, Xue
A1  - Celotto, Stefano
A1  - Pizzol, Damiano
A1  - Gasevic, Danijela
A1  - Ji, Meng-Meng
A1  - Barnini, Tommaso
A1  - Solmi, Marco
A1  - Stubbs, Brendon
A1  - Smith, Lee
A1  - Lopez Sanchez, Guillermo F
A1  - Pesolillo, Gabriella
