T1  - Vitamin D supplementation prior to in vitro fertilisation in women with polycystic ovary syndrome: a protocol of a multicentre randomised, double-blind, placebo-controlled clinical trial.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1136/bmjopen-2020-041409
A1  - Hu, Kai-Lun
A1  - Gan, Kwanghann
A1  - Wang, Rui
A1  - Li, Wentao
A1  - Wu, Qiongfang
A1  - Zheng, Beihong
