T3  - Comment on: J Am Acad Child Adolesc Psychiatry. 2017 Oct;56(10):849-856.e6 PMID: 28942807 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/28942807] Comment on: J Am Acad Child Adolesc Psychiatry. 2018 Oct;57(10):792-793 PMID: 30274654 [https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/30274654]
