T1  - Increased rates of complications in singleton pregnancies of women previously diagnosed with polycystic ovary syndrome predominantly in the hyperandrogenic phenotype.
DO  - https://dx.doi.org/10.1016/j.fertnstert.2017.06.015
A1  - de Wilde, Marlieke A
A1  - Lamain-de Ruiter, Marije
A1  - Veltman-Verhulst, Susanne M
A1  - Kwee, Anneke
A1  - Laven, Joop S
